          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>meat-free sausages </strong>and break into bite-sized pieces with a wooden spoon and cook for 2-4 min or until crispy</p><p>Once crispy, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>and <strong>sliced apple </strong>and cook for 6-7 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-42-1705052331109-x200.jpg",
